trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref uid="langword_csharp_typeof" name="typeof" href=""></xref> expression, an expression that returns a <xref:System.Type> for a specified type name.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_typeof" name="typeof" href=""> </xref> 식, 반환 하는 식은 <xref:System.Type>지정된 된 형식 이름에 대 한.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A CodeTypeOfExpression represents a `typeof` expression that returns a <xref:System.Type> at runtime.
The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeOfExpression.Type%2A> property specifies the data type to return a <xref:System.Type> object for.

Use <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression> to represent source code that refers to a type by name, such as when creating a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCastExpression> to cast an object to a name-specified type.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여 <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression>와 같은 이름으로 참조 형식에는 소스 코드를 만들 때는 <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCastExpression>이름이 지정 된 형식으로 개체를 캐스팅 하.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCastExpression> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceExpression>
